    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>迎接灵界来客</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>两位全新英雄和四把全新武器将加入你的冒险旅程中。每个英雄都有其独特的玩法和战斗技巧，四把新鲜出炉的武器也将带给你截然不同的战斗体验！</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>操纵两位全新英雄</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>行者：拔出毫毛化作分身，根据手持武器特性打击敌人；或使用镇妖索吸取敌人真气，强化自身武器！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2111850/extras/ad3086ede4c61b45842e9971f2b7f76d.poster.avif?t=1702456074\" width=400 height=226 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2111850/extras/ad3086ede4c61b45842e9971f2b7f76d.webm?t=1702456074\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2111850/extras/ad3086ede4c61b45842e9971f2b7f76d.mp4?t=1702456074\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br></li><li>璃：驭使火狐、召唤火陨，用无尽的火焰吞噬眼前的一切敌人。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2111850/extras/b1d61c4a2a4ef685dcaacf1326b166f9.poster.avif?t=1702456074\" width=400 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2111850/extras/b1d61c4a2a4ef685dcaacf1326b166f9.webm?t=1702456074\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2111850/extras/b1d61c4a2a4ef685dcaacf1326b166f9.mp4?t=1702456074\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>解锁四把全新武器</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>六方：阻挡面前的一切攻击，随后将所有伤害悉数奉还。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2111850/extras/5691756b9c191ee561fc74fb0f4d122e.poster.avif?t=1702456074\" width=400 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2111850/extras/5691756b9c191ee561fc74fb0f4d122e.webm?t=1702456074\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2111850/extras/5691756b9c191ee561fc74fb0f4d122e.mp4?t=1702456074\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br></li><li>织云：操纵数把灵针灵动游走于敌人之间，取敌将首级于瞬息之间。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2111850/extras/4b04bed7c87a0ba10a185bcb65c14af7.poster.avif?t=1702456074\" width=400 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2111850/extras/4b04bed7c87a0ba10a185bcb65c14af7.webm?t=1702456074\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2111850/extras/4b04bed7c87a0ba10a185bcb65c14af7.mp4?t=1702456074\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br></li><li>弧光：触发不计其数的闪电链，同时打击成片敌人。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2111850/extras/c85385d6fdc6f0184746a9c2d6f962d7.poster.avif?t=1702456074\" width=400 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2111850/extras/c85385d6fdc6f0184746a9c2d6f962d7.webm?t=1702456074\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2111850/extras/c85385d6fdc6f0184746a9c2d6f962d7.mp4?t=1702456074\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br></li><li>雷刹：唯一一把能向你的队友开枪的武器：可以施加护盾保护队友，也能对敌人打出高暴击倍率伤害！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2111850/extras/178db2faa44bb4e652b60364939832a3.poster.avif?t=1702456074\" width=400 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2111850/extras/178db2faa44bb4e652b60364939832a3.webm?t=1702456074\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2111850/extras/178db2faa44bb4e652b60364939832a3.mp4?t=1702456074\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></li></ul><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >关于《枪火重生》</h2></strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>《枪火重生》是一款融合了第一人称射击、Roguelite随机元素和RPG策略选择的冒险闯关游戏。玩家在游戏里可以操纵不同能力的英雄组建多种Build玩法，使用随机掉落的武器在随机性关卡中进行冒险挑战。可以单人畅玩，也可以最多四人组队挑战。<br></li><li>在游戏中，玩家的每次关卡体验都是随机的。每一次重新开始游戏都是新的体验。你可以在不同的关卡体验中遇见不同的英雄天赋、武器道具、不同的关卡路线和战斗节奏。<br></li><li><i>如果你有任何问题、反馈，可以将Steam名字、问题的具体描述或截图发送到 <a href=\"mailto:qhstaff@2980.com\">qhstaff@2980.com</a> ，我们会第一时间检查并定位问题。</i></li></ul>",
